| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7724 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2a7f533b-40f0-5463-a9d0-df2f44b1aeaf"
